ey_kaczynski_px.png" src="https://img2.storyblok.com/36x0/filters:format(png):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/630x630/2941b3592a/757ab7bc-1ade-41c6-a059-db20895227c2_kelsey_kaczynski_px.png" class="lazy undefined"></picture> <!----> <!----></div> <p class="font-500 text-[12px] text-light-gray leading-[20px] tracking-[0.4px] md:text-[16px] md:leading-[24px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">
